  "texts": [
    "The initial stage involves data acquisition, where RGB-D and depth camera data are collected as the foundational input for subsequent stages.",
    "Moving on to the second stage, processing of RGB-D details was activated.",
    "During this phase, tasks include feature extraction and pairwise matching while simultaneously addressing depth-related activities, such as storing point clouds, and aligning lines or shapes.",
    "In the third stage, activities such as noise removal and semantic segmentation (SS), in addition to loop closure detection, are performed to lay the groundwork for map construction.",
    "The fourth stage is dedicated to focus on pose estimation and optimization techniques, leading to improvement in the accuracy of the system output."
